headline: Quanta Services price target lowered to $398 from $399 at Truist
summary: Truist lowered the firm’s price target on Quanta Services (PWR) to $398 from $399 and keeps a Buy rating on the shares as part of a broader research note previewing Q4 results for Machinery, Infrastructure Services, and Multi-Industry / Industrial Technology names.
